title: Episode 375: Just Got Cancelled (Feat. Toosii)
itunes:title: Episode 375: Just Got Cancelled (Feat. Toosii)
description:
Singer/rapper, Toosii joined the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest EP 'Boys Don't Cry.' Toosii admits his wrongdoings after taking his relationship issues to social media, he discusses how he took accountability for this, and how he's moving forward. Toosii opens up about fatherhood, dispels rumors about his sexuality, his future roleplaying ideas in the bedroom, and much more. Enjoy!
